OL,3,CMan jailed for 25 years for repeatedly
OL,4,Craping two children
OL,6,FA man from Swansea has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto 25 years in jail after he was found
OL,8,Fguilty of historically raping two
OL,9,Fgirls under the age of 16.
OL,11,FDavid Lake, 57, from Llansamlet,
OL,12,Fcarried out repeated attacks on two
OL,13,Fchildren, who are now adults.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
