OL,3,CMan jailed for 25 years for repeatedly
OL,4,Craping two children
OL,6,FIn April, Lake was found guilty of one
OL,7,Fcount of rape of a female under 16,
OL,8,Ffour counts of indecent assault on a
OL,9,Fgirl under the age of 14 years, one
OL,10,Fcount of unlawful sexual intercourse
OL,11,Fwith a girl under 13 years of age, and
OL,12,Fone count of attempt to indecently
OL,13,Fassault a girl under the age of 16.
OL,15,FHe will be on the sex offenders
OL,16,Fregister for life.
OL,18,FSioned Davies, Detective Constable for
OL,19,FSouth Wales Police, praised the
OL,20,Fbravery of the victims in coming
OL,21,Fforward.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
