OL,3,CMan jailed for 25 years for repeatedly
OL,4,Craping two children
OL,6,FIn a statement, she said: "It took an
OL,7,Funbelievable amount of strength and
OL,8,Fcourage for David Lake's victims to
OL,9,Fconfide to someone else about the
OL,10,Fcrimes he carried out upon them,
OL,11,Fespecially with so many years having
OL,12,Fpassed in-between.
OL,14,F"This was a long and complex
OL,15,Finvestigation which has finally
OL,16,Fresulted in David Lake being brought
OL,17,Fto justice, and the severity of his
OL,18,Foffending is reflected in the size of
OL,19,Fhis sentence.
