PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779207074
OL,3,CMan jailed for 25 years for repeatedly
OL,4,Craping two children
OL,6,F"David Lake's attacks on the victims
OL,7,Fwere only stopped when he went to jail
OL,8,Ffor a separate matter. With this
OL,9,Fsentence, we hope that his offending
OL,10,Fhas now been stopped for good."
